stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PENDING: create()
    PENDING --> RUNNING: worker 启动
    RUNNING --> COMPLETED: 正常完成
    RUNNING --> FAILED: 异常退出
    RUNNING --> INTERRUPTED: cancel(action=interrupt)
    RUNNING --> CANCELLED: cancel(action=rollback)

    INTERRUPTED --> RUNNING: 用户恢复
    INTERRUPTED --> [*]: 超时清理

    COMPLETED --> [*]
    FAILED --> [*]
    CANCELLED --> [*]

    note right of RUNNING
        worker: run_agent()
        stream: SSE 实时推送
        journal: RunJournal 事件收集
    end note

    note right of CANCELLED
        rollback: 恢复 pre-run checkpoint
        cleanup: 释放沙箱资源
    end note
